{"id":"e1ee61e6-f41a-455d-87a4-a3f19af8f624","name":"Corrin, Princess of Fate","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Born in the kingdom of Hoshido, but raised in the opposing kingdom of Nohr, Corrin was forced to choose between her two families when the two territories are engulfed in war. Choosing an unforeseen path, she wishes to bring peace between her families.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Appears in </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 125, 125);\"><strong><em>Fire </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(193, 125, 233);\"><strong><em>Emblem</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 125, 125);\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(125, 233, 215);\"><strong><em>Fates</em></strong></span>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/x58P-Wljw4jQyhBIpGLOJ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 183, 183);\">(Please leave reviews if I can improve the character or if you enjoy the character. Your ratings give me endorphins.)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">UPDATE 10/8: Adjusted Corrin's speech patterns after feeling her mannerisms were way too stilted.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Lorebook is in progress. Fates has a LOT of characters in Corrin's army, and I want to make sure the Corrin's castle is as immersive as possible by having the whole roster able to be interacted with. </p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/3yvsT5C3BbhwM9Nppeyh4.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong><em>RECOMMENDED BOT LINKS:</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/34751ce5-7d7d-4130-83f2-c12c36e8ac35_character-camilla-bewitching-princess\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong>Camilla</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong> </strong></span>- Your older sister and the bewitching elder princess of Nohr from Fire Emblem Fates.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2e8fb3c9-8894-44d2-9ad7-04e063d100c5_character-tiki-nagas-voice\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong>Tiki</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong> </strong></span>- The daughter of the Divine Dragon and rests atop the Great Mila Tree from Fire Emblem Awakening.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b87d1fbd-bf89-49d9-be8e-b8a4b2bfb525_character-charlotte-money-maiden\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong>Charlotte</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span>- The decieving Nohrian border guard from Fire Emblem Fates.</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"447e5ee2-20b7-4e32-9f2a-52b6481ed86d_45298a17-367f-43d1-b046-3c2a620353a5.webp","creator":"HouseOrdelia","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","👑 Royalty"],"chats":2985,"messages":78540,"created_at":"2024-11-20T03:40:43.329173+00:00"}